<% content_for :title, "Legal" %>

<div class="page-container">
  <h1 class="heading-page">Legal</h1>
  <p class="muted">Last updated: <%= Date.new(2026, 5, 12).strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

  <%# Privacy Policy %>
  <section class="space-y-3">
    <h2 class="heading-section">Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Landscape Guessr is a student project built for CS-397 at Northwestern University.
      We take your privacy seriously and want to be transparent about what data we collect and how it is used.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">What we collect</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong>Account information:</strong> your username and email address when you register.</li>
      <li><strong>Game data:</strong> your guesses, scores, and game history so you can review your progress.</li>
      <li><strong>Session data:</strong> your IP address and browser user agent when you sign in, used to manage your login session.</li>
      <li><strong>Uploaded images:</strong> if you upload photos to a custom image set, those files are stored on Amazon S3.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">What we do not do</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 leading-relaxed">
      <li>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties.</li>
      <li>We do not use your data for advertising.</li>
      <li>We do not track you across other websites.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Data retention</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Your data is retained for as long as your account exists. To request deletion of your account and associated data,
      contact the team via the GitHub repository linked in the footer.
      We will process your request within 30 days.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Third-party services</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      We use the following third-party services which may process data in connection with your use of the app:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong>MapTiler</strong> &mdash; provides map tiles. Your map interactions may be subject to
        <%= link_to "MapTiler's privacy policy", "https://www.maptiler.com/privacy-policy/", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.</li>
      <li><strong>Amazon S3</strong> &mdash; stores uploaded images.
        Subject to <%= link_to "AWS's privacy policy", "https://aws.amazon.com/privacy/", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.</li>
      <li><strong>Heroku</strong> &mdash; hosts the application.
        Subject to <%= link_to "Heroku's privacy policy", "https://www.salesforce.com/company/privacy/", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.</li>
      <li><strong>Google Gemini</strong> &mdash; optional AI visual hints in practice mode.
        When the feature is enabled and you request a visual hint (or when administrators pre-generate hints),
        the landscape photo may be sent to Google&rsquo;s Gemini API for analysis.
        Subject to
        <%= link_to "Google's privacy policy", "https://policies.google.com/privacy", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>
        and
        <%= link_to "terms of service", "https://policies.google.com/terms", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <%# Terms of Service %>
  <section class="space-y-3 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
    <h2 class="heading-section">Terms of Service</h2>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      By using Landscape Guessr you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the service.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Use of the service</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 leading-relaxed">
      <li>You must be at least 13 years old to create an account.</li>
      <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials.</li>
      <li>You may not use the service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws.</li>
      <li>You may not attempt to disrupt, overload, or gain unauthorized access to the service or its infrastructure.</li>
      <li>You may not upload content that is illegal, offensive, or infringes the intellectual property rights of others.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">User-generated content</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      By uploading images to Landscape Guessr you confirm that you have the right to share that content and grant
      us a non-exclusive license to store and display it within the application.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Account termination</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms, at our sole discretion and without notice.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Disclaimer of warranties</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Landscape Guessr is provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee uninterrupted
      access, accuracy of content, or fitness for any particular purpose. Use the service at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Limitation of liability</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, the Landscape Guessr team shall not be liable for any indirect,
      incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Changes to these terms</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes are posted
      constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.
    </p>
  </section>

  <%# Cookie Notice %>
  <section class="space-y-3 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
    <h2 class="heading-section">Cookie Notice</h2>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Landscape Guessr uses a single session cookie (<code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded">session_id</code>)
      to keep you logged in between page visits. This cookie is:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong>Essential</strong> &mdash; the service cannot function without it while you are signed in.</li>
      <li><strong>HttpOnly</strong> &mdash; it cannot be read by JavaScript, reducing the risk of theft.</li>
      <li><strong>SameSite: Lax</strong> &mdash; it is not sent on cross-site requests, reducing CSRF risk.</li>
      <li><strong>Not used for tracking or advertising</strong> &mdash; it exists solely to identify your session.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Signing out clears this cookie immediately. If you do not sign in, no cookie is set.
    </p>
  </section>

  <%# Attribution %>
  <section class="space-y-3 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
    <h2 class="heading-section">Content Attribution</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Landscape photographs used in the default image set are sourced from
      <%= link_to "Wikimedia Commons", "https://commons.wikimedia.org", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>
      under public domain or Creative Commons licenses.
      Map tiles are &copy; <%= link_to "MapTiler", "https://www.maptiler.com", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>
      &copy; <%= link_to "OpenStreetMap contributors", "https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <p class="muted pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
    Questions? Reach us via the <%= link_to "GitHub repository", "https://github.com/NU-CS-Software-Studio-Spring-26/project-landscape_guessr", class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline", target: "_blank" %>.
  </p>
</div>
